{"tid":1795059,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共搜刮民脂圖挽劣勢","createTime":"2019-12-23T15:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T15:26:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"67e85d0c67de218f89b0d1281e16fcced899a6cc","tid":1795059,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:05:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191223/2FSVJGMYWATEBTILQKA3PVBXVU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191223%2F2FSVJGMYWATEBTILQKA3PVBXVU%2F&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpprbLZzzsfwfKyNyJagnZM4%3D&h=74d4ef31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191223%2F2FSVJGMYWATEBTILQKA3PVBXVU%2F&h=d62f9bf0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191223/2FSVJGMYWATEBTILQKA3PVBXVU/</a><br />\n<br />\n中共搜刮民脂圖挽劣勢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191223/large/1577033618_2609.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191223%2Flarge%2F1577033618_2609.jpg&h=4c265bff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬化騰<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】國進民退的政策下，民營大企的負責人近年接連卸任或退休。這是對中國龐大的民營企業施加更大控制力的最新舉措，完全沒有出現1950年代公私合營運動引起全社會歡迎的場面，而是引起極多批判，認為這是在「殺豬、明目張膽地搶私企財物、搜刮民脂民膏」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巨頭接連「退休」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：內地客蝕沽港豪宅套現<br />\n<br />\n政商緊密關係是民企賺錢的不二法門，然而伴君如伴虎，阿里巴巴創辦人馬雲今年9月10日「退休」後，有指一度拒交客戶貸款數據給中共的騰訊創辦人馬化騰，也於同月20日卸任騰訊徵信法定代理人。聯想創辦人柳傳志在屢被傳遭中共逼退後，日前也宣佈卸任聯想控股公司法定代表人和董事職位。<br />\n<br />\n即使馬雲、馬化騰都是中共黨員，而且中共已在民企設黨委支部，惟中共還是不放心，以致杭州市今年9月派出100名幹部進駐100間民營重點企業，為期一年，其中阿里巴巴也在列。旅美政論作家陳破空早前分析認為，中國經濟下滑，中共已對民企動了殺心，力圖掠奪私有財產，「豬養肥了就要殺」。開元資本董事總經理西弗斯（Brock Silvers）預計其他製造業密集型地區也將很快採取類似政策。<br />\n<br />\n國務院副總理劉鶴去年指出，民企在中國貢獻了50%以上的稅收、60%以上的GDP、70%以上的專利發明權，以及80%以上的城鎮就業人口。若國進民退持續，讓國營資金或黨營資金入股，導致公司控制權混亂，從實績來看，無法改善績效，這也將會影響市場，經濟更難突破發展。"},{"pid":"14373e9e0d6615947e301c81aeb99357e5327845","tid":1795059,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:06:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">X&rsquo;MAS EVE 願平安歸香港🇭🇰</span><br />\n日期 : 12月24日 (二)<br />\n時間：19:00 - 22:00<br />\n地點：<br />\n元朗yoho<br />\n沙田 新城市<br />\n尖沙咀 海港城<br />\n旺角 朗豪坊<br />\n銅鑼灣 時代廣場<br />\nLink : @xmasevehkchannel"},{"pid":"9f61ee2659321d9bef8cc087052d374dabc077a8","tid":1795059,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:08:55.000Z","msg":"班野都係同支共勾結先可以做大<br />\n算吧啦 黑吃黑姐"},{"pid":"22a7d6b45bf55662eebb9756b1df8b256aab4caa","tid":1795059,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:20:12.000Z","msg":"小學生真係唔識，當變左官員外人管，間企業一定唔會再諗點創新(雖然都係抄)同賺錢"},{"pid":"6ec4693862798225c67e7af4e4170dd51d69707a","tid":1795059,"uid":267915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:20:37.000Z","msg":"借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［5%捐獻師2.0] 聖誕和你捐challenge<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1794786\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1794786</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PUMrN35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPUMrN35.jpg&h=34703016&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sbtBqQN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsbtBqQN.jpg&h=44c23cba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7e20f3aff742cbe22c8eab3f0c23e43bb1ab92b","tid":1795059,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:26:25.000Z","msg":"所以諗諗下2022佢搞冬奧都幾好, 嘔唔到錢, 爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}